  "title": "Temp Admin",
  "description": "<p>1. Must be able to extract data from excel output tables to Powerpoint charts.</p><p>2. Must be able to understand how to edit the charts in Powerpoint.</p><p>3. Must be meticulous and good with numbers.</p><p>4. Proficient in Excel and Microsoft Powerpoint as the reports relies heavily on them.</p><p>5. Possess positive attitude and enjoys report charting.</p><p>6. Has an eye for details.</p><p>7. IT savvy.</p><p>8. Not required to run any analysis.</p><p>Period of engagement: 23 February - 20 March 2026 </p><p>Location: Office </p><p>Working hours: Monday - Friday, 9am - 6pm (less 1 hour lunch break)</p>",
