    "description": "<p>BEACON CONSULTING PTE LTD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Beacon, a rapidly-growing SME, has been driven by a purpose: inspiring people and organisations to create a better tomorrow, beyond commercial success. We are honoured to be recognised as a \"Company of Good\" in 2024. This is a testament to our dedication to this purpose.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>In recent years, we're focusing on making a lasting impact in three key areas:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Thriving People: We foster a workplace that champions personal growth, innovation, and collaboration. We believe in the power of every voice and provide opportunities for all Beaconites to reach their full potential.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Empowered Clients: We go beyond traditional client relationships, building partnerships to develop solutions that truly work. We offer holistic support through advisory services, learning opportunities, and insightful data analysis.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Sustainable Future: Our vision of a \"better tomorrow\" extends to society. We address pressing social issues like disability and aging, while actively promoting diversity, equity, and inclusion. Additionally, we champion environmental responsibility with eco-friendly initiatives, ensuring a healthy planet for future generations.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
